  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Application is irresponsive when opening transaction details in offline mode\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nBeing offline should not prevent user from seeing transaction details\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/32101444-eaf59d80-bb20-11e7-8e2c-a8e0f4cbd5aa.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Request some ETH via faucet and make sure balance is updated\r\n- Turn off internet and open transaction details in transaction history\r\n- Try to navigate to any other screen\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n* Status version: last seen in `0.9.12`\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n",
